data.description: Manufactured home that is on a 1.35 acre lot. Large kitchen with plenty of countertop space. Three nice size bedrooms plenty of closet space. Two living areas. Nice deck out front to set out on or sit out back in your covered screened porch. Also a large storage shed conveys with the home. AC condenser and heat pump are 4 years old. **$5,000 repair allowance with an acceptable offer!
